{"tid":1667290,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我發覺我地唔覺意搵到點嬴區選!!!!!!!!!","createTime":"2019-10-21T11:21:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T12:01:39.000Z","uid":268746,"like":46,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"9686ab1f96eafb1072965d0b275c2f6f6427cf32","tid":1667290,"uid":268746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:21:03.000Z","msg":"就係靠大家口耳相傳，叫身邊嘅人幫手做助選團!<br />\n<br />\n大家好，我地係一個新組織 - 區義員(社區義工動員)。<br />\n係為咗幫一班唔夠資源嘅區選候選人，去招募大量義工助選。<br />\n我地唔屬於任何一個候選人，只要收到同路人嘅請求，就會公佈消息等大家自己去揀，幾點、幫邊個、點樣幫，完全由義工自行去選擇。<br />\n<br />\n正正所有義工都可以靈活參與，所以我地稱自己為Watlunteer(流水式助選團)<br />\n我地想動員埋一班一直想為抗爭出力，偏偏由因為各種原因唔能夠走上街頭嘅人，例如銀髮族同主婦。你地正正就係候選人最想得到嘅人力資源!<br />\n<br />\n成功從來唔係靠一條路，街頭有街頭戰線，制度有制度嘅戰線，只有兄弟爬山，各自努力先可以全方位去取得成功。<br />\n<br />\n因此，我希望大家可以響應我地嘅號召。得閒嘅，幫手去做助選義工，或者幫手叫身邊人，幫手叫屋企人，一齊參與其事。<br />\n<br />\nJoin我地Tg，<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NbG1JhMvR5JYHd_IscsNJQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNbG1JhMvR5JYHd_IscsNJQ&d=bp2T%2F%2B5c5q8hcpZmRI3qNn4WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=85b00a90\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/NbG1JhMvR5JYHd_IscsNJQ</a><br />\n或者FB<br />\n再將我地介紹俾身邊想出力，<br />\n但落唔到街頭嘅人。<br />\n<br />\n區選只剩返1個月，多你一個真係好多!<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PXJMxgn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPXJMxgn.jpg&h=fe490ba8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2kgeF9J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2kgeF9J.jpg&h=221e318a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AvXA924.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAvXA924.jpg&h=2b0ef7fa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/424LNPL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F424LNPL.jpg&h=c78f0087&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fa2ce3076e77822050efcbffd6d0cd0c34bb8e76","tid":1667290,"uid":268746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:21:59.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"b3e95d5db04a5df900ca4e2f1988f5248ca41ef0","tid":1667290,"uid":268746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:24:49.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"77ba9757015c36ec898ba1acde41109efe4c9618","tid":1667290,"uid":156253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:25:08.000Z","msg":"加油!加入"},{"pid":"aaf4d3d7bb6c768e1bd5242b7f86ec537421bf3b","tid":1667290,"uid":3776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:26:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1dbd67e850ed7b99fd4ec0bc72d9657f51a0fe61","tid":1667290,"uid":274732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:26:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幫推"},{"pid":"ef8c0f3eadd96e147dbe38838d6d56f74e0046eb","tid":1667290,"uid":268746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:26:26.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"2db8b791bc7b8ce87d759fa38b3f4e4eb3c2100d","tid":1667290,"uid":268746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:28:53.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"4567adb94aa07487f4402a885e94a68d0f4a9e5c","tid":1667290,"uid":268746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:29:37.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"e09cb9d1549941731db127bc3edfb56a9c22dff0","tid":1667290,"uid":148795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:30:10.000Z","msg":"幫你推"},{"pid":"07070cfa1149060c810afc0109008765347bb55b","tid":1667290,"uid":208251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:30:46.000Z","msg":"推，自己香港自己救"},{"pid":"7818a7c01f9a5a7be7839fa7d520543f13f8a29a","tid":1667290,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:31:25.000Z","msg":"[實用]    香城online防具升級詳細篇<br />\n<br />\n近呢一個月，我見到多左好多新入香城online嘅玩家，勇武/和理非都有好多工作做，鑑於有好多人唔知點配搭防具，眼見好多手足都只用貴價6092X，除左冇必要之外仲晒左好多錢，故此我係度再講一次點去配合適的防具。<br />\n<br />\n防毒面具：<br />\n中後/後防(物資站/噴漆師/文宣組/美化工程組/網上資訊組)<br />\n首選最合符經濟效益<br />\n包括單咀<br />\n3200/HF-52+3311K-55<br />\n一set最平100港幣有找<br />\n雙咀：<br />\n6200+6001/6003/6005(6005唔需要特登買，成本價貴)+5n11/5p71(唔建議5p71,如果要嘅不如買502再搭P100綿抵啲)+501蓋<br />\n例如：6200+6001CN+5n11+501 我見100已經有一set<br />\n而且 就算唔用5n11同501蓋 都ok 6001CN一對最平$30，我見$50通常都有<br />\n6003貴少少 $70成平價(睇你有冇運見到)<br />\n以上都可以頂到TG，但記得聞到味要即換<br />\n<br />\n想了解更多快啲入去連登睇啦😛<br />\n...<br />\n防毒面具篇完<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1666931\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1666931</a>"},{"pid":"54d92bb72bc7de7e1432d98d4bad61ff2a902daf","tid":1667290,"uid":268746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:32:41.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a492408c900257d951724e5a151281f48e8f52e5","tid":1667290,"uid":22310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:33:50.000Z","msg":"好東西推"},{"pid":"5ad8b4a09720c7ccdb0c0b25a9b33a8dc0090ac9","tid":1667290,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:35:40.000Z","msg":"第三張又畀連登啲民主派 haters 鬧了<br />\n<br />\n係泛民<br />\nnot 民主派"},{"pid":"04952168d6af6db9ac13e1c995d3eaa8ad871396","tid":1667290,"uid":9347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:40:42.000Z","msg":"一定要推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97f54945283d42fa1cba28f4ea6cb6f9bfe84cd2","tid":1667290,"uid":268746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:43:08.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"4bad8201413f5691b9e2d9b165f241f5ec1ba9f3","tid":1667290,"uid":292722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:43:44.000Z","msg":"唔錯呀個idea!!!"},{"pid":"13ccec64abe98d300c27852940d5ef62abdf70e6","tid"